TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed NetworkInterfaceType extends System.Enum

summary.span: 指定網路介面的類型。

span.span: Specifies types of network interfaces.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 網路介面，也稱為網路介面卡，將電腦連線到網路。Network interfaces, also known as network adapters, connect a computer to a network. 介面型別定義傳輸媒體提供網路連線能力。The interface type defines the transmission media that provides network connectivity. 這個列舉會定義所傳回的值屬性。This enumeration defines the values returned by the property.

AsymmetricDsl = 94

summary.span: ISDN 是透過電話線的一組資料傳輸標準。

span.span: ISDN is a set of standards for data transmission over telephone lines.
